Package: posterpoller
Title: Seamless open-source poster voting for conferences powered by Google Forms
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Candace", "Savonen", , 
    c("cansav09@gmail.com","csavonen@fredhutch.org"), 
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Use Google forms to allow voting for posters at conferences using QR-codes. This package helps you automatically set that up for easy polling. 
